V3.44Beta6.3 E & V3.44Beta7 - 07/09/99 Kicked 'F4' & 'F5' text from the helpzone !!!
V3.44Beta6.4 E & V3.44Beta8 - 07/11/99 New routine MOVELINE. If 1 line is removed, the rest moves up.
